      • updateConcept

        public LatticeWrapper updateConcept(ConceptWrapper concept)
                             throws java.lang.NullPointerException
        Updates a Concept (for example concept name, description, is this concept part of the taxonomy, ...). Since Changes to a concept can have effects on other concepts part of a Domain the whole domain needs to be updated and returned to ensure current data.
        Parameters:
        concept - the concept to update -- wrapped i a helper class reducing overhead
        Returns:
        the updated domain this concept belongs to
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if the Concept is not in the database
